    "course_title": "CLINICAL DECISION MAKING: NEUROMUSCULAR MECHANICS AND CONTROL",
    "description": "Addresses the mechanics and control of the neuromuscular and skeletal systems as they relate to human movement. Neural control of movement is discussed in detail with specific emphasis on theories underlying recruitment of muscle in health and disease.",
